metadata.name: Icy Cream Club # 01
metadata.description:
In the light of the recent events we've decided to show our full support to the Ukrainian people in the best way we can.
As a token of admiration and respect 
We'll be releasing 10 different commemorative Icy's which will give immediate access to our main community-based project and 1 WL Spot for the Collection
.
100% of sales are destinated to support UKR artists and humanitarian causes.
Help us to help others, be part of it.
